   <taskbody>
      <context class="- topic/section task/context ">The <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Workflow Settings</uicontrol> page enables you to define the settings related to workflow transitions.</context>
      <steps class="- topic/ol task/steps ">
         <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">In the module menu, click <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Administration</uicontrol>.</cmd>
            <info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info ">The <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">ADMINISTRATION</uicontrol> page is displayed.</info>
         </step>
         <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">In the navigation pane, expand <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">System Configurations</uicontrol>, and then click <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Workflow Settings</uicontrol>.</cmd>
            <info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info ">The <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">WORKFLOW SETTINGS</uicontrol> page is displayed.</info>
         </step>
         <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Provide the required information in the fields, as described in the following table.</cmd>
            <info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info ">
               <table colsep="1" rowsep="1" class="- topic/table ">
                  <tgroup cols="2" class="- topic/tgroup ">
                     <colspec colname="c1" colnum="1" colwidth="30%" class="- topic/colspec "/>
                     <colspec colname="c2" colnum="2" colwidth="70%" class="- topic/colspec "/>
                     <thead class="- topic/thead ">
                        <row class="- topic/row ">
                           <entry class="- topic/entry ">Field Name</entry>
                           <entry class="- topic/entry ">Description</entry>
                        </row>
                     </thead>
                     <tbody class="- topic/tbody ">
                        <row class="- topic/row ">
                           <entry class="- topic/entry ">Max size of Document to attach during Workflow action (in MB)</entry>
                           <entry class="- topic/entry ">Enter the maximum size of the attachment that can be uploaded during a workflow transition.<note class="- topic/note "> For attachments during workflow transitions, this value takes precedence over the maximum file size defined in the <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Max allowable Document Size in Attachment (in MB)</uicontrol> in the <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Application Settings</uicontrol> page. <ph product="Exclude_PG_Content" class="- topic/ph ">For information on application settings, refer to <xref href="App_Settings.dita" class="- topic/xref "/>.</ph>
                              </note>
                           </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row class="- topic/row ">
                           <entry class="- topic/entry ">Default Mail Body Template for Workflow Notification</entry>
                           <entry class="- topic/entry ">Select the appropriate mail body template to send a standard automated email notification to the action stakeholders of the subsequent stage whenever the workflow action is performed. â€‹<p class="- topic/p ">Available options are templates defined for the form in the <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Mail Body Templates</uicontrol> catalog of the library.</p>
                           </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row class="- topic/row ">
                           <entry class="- topic/entry ">Default Days to Complete an Action</entry>
                           <entry class="- topic/entry ">Enter the number of days before which an action must be performed in the current workflow stage. When you configure properties for a workflow stage, the defined number is used as a default. <ph product="Exclude_PG_Content" class="- topic/ph ">For information on creating workflows, refer to <xref href="../Configuration_Toolkit/Workflow_Management/CreateWF.dita"
                                       class="- topic/xref ">Creating a Workflow</xref>.</ph>
                           </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row class="- topic/row ">
                           <entry class="- topic/entry ">Send a reminder prior to due date</entry>
                           <entry class="- topic/entry ">Select the check box to send a reminder email to the stakeholders with the due date details.</entry>
                        </row>
                        <row class="- topic/row ">
                           <entry class="- topic/entry ">Number Of Days</entry>
                           <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                              <note class="- topic/note ">This field is displayed if the <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Send a reminder prior to due date</uicontrol> check box is selected.</note>
                              <p class="- topic/p ">Enter the number of days prior to due date on which a reminder email is sent to the action stakeholders with the due date details. The due date is defined in the <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Days to Complete</uicontrol> field in the stage properties pane of the <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Workflow Management</uicontrol> page. <ph product="Exclude_PG_Content" class="- topic/ph ">For information on creating workflows, refer to <xref href="../Configuration_Toolkit/Workflow_Management/CreateWFSimple.dita"
                                          class="- topic/xref ">Creating a Workflow</xref>.</ph>
                              </p>
                           </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row class="- topic/row ">
                           <entry class="- topic/entry ">Select Template</entry>
                           <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                              <note class="- topic/note ">This field is displayed if the <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Send a reminder prior to due date</uicontrol> check box is selected.</note>
                              <p class="- topic/p ">Select the appropriate mail body template for the reminder email. Available options are templates defined for the form in the <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Mail Body Templates</uicontrol> catalog of the library. </p>
                           </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row class="- topic/row ">
                           <entry class="- topic/entry ">Send reminder to action stakeholders past due date</entry>
                           <entry class="- topic/entry ">Select the check box to send a reminder email after the due date is crossed if the stakeholder does not perform a workflow action. The due date is defined in the <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Days to Complete</uicontrol> field in the stage properties pane of the <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Workflow Management</uicontrol> page. <ph product="Exclude_PG_Content" class="- topic/ph ">For information on creating workflows, refer to <xref href="../Configuration_Toolkit/Workflow_Management/CreateWFSimple.dita"
                                       class="- topic/xref ">Creating a Workflow</xref>.</ph>
                           </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row class="- topic/row ">
                           <entry class="- topic/entry ">Select Template</entry>
                           <entry class="- topic/entry ">
                              <note class="- topic/note ">This field is displayed if the <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Send reminder to action stakeholders past due date</uicontrol> check box is selected.</note>
                              <p class="- topic/p ">Select the appropriate mail body template for the reminder email. Available options are templates defined for the form in the <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Mail Body Templates</uicontrol> catalog of the library. </p>
                           </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row class="- topic/row ">
                           <entry class="- topic/entry ">Show Workflow History in Details Report</entry>
                           <entry class="- topic/entry ">Select the check box to add the <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Workflow History</uicontrol> section in the <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Details Report</uicontrol>.</entry>
                        </row>
                     </tbody>
                  </tgroup>
               </table>
            </info>
         </step>
         <step class="- topic/li task/step ">
            <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Click <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Save</uicontrol>.</cmd>
         </step>
